Standardized Plots for Presentation of MSE Results in IOTC

Iago Mosqueira (EC JRC) iago.mosqueira@ec.europa.eu

29 October, 2021

Source: vignettes/iotcplots.Rmd
iotcplots.Rmd

license: Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International Public License

Inputs

Performance levels across MPs

These are the necessary columns in the performance data.frame

  • indicator, indicator code
  • year
  • data, computed value
  • iter, iteration number
  • name, indicator name
  • mp, MP name

  • mp, MP name
  • year
  • data, computed value
  • iter, iteration number
  • qname, computed metric, e.g. Catch (C), mean F (F)
